When `.cursor/goal/active.json` exists and has `"status": "active"`, read it before working.

Prefer autonomous iteration toward the objective. Do not claim completion until the configured verifier passes. If the Goal Loop stop hook sends a follow-up, inspect the referenced log and address the root cause before ending the turn again.
